**INSTALLATION OSMOCOM 2G + OPEN5GS 4G LTE**

Ubuntu 24.04 LTS x86_64  |  IP : 10.0.0.1  |  MCC : 547

*Document de synthese complet — Mai 2026*

Version 2.0  |  MNC = PLACEHOLDER  |  ARFCN = PLACEHOLDER

# **PARTIE 1 — OSMOCOM 2G**

## **Etape 1/6 — Mise a jour systeme + depot sysmocom + dependances**

### **Bloc 1 — Mise a jour systeme**

| sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y |
| --- |

### **Bloc 2 — Prerequis depot**

| sudo apt install -y \ |
| --- |
| wget curl gnupg2 ca-certificates \ |
| apt-transport-https software-properties-common \ |
| lsb-release |

### **Bloc 3 — Cle GPG sysmocom**

| wget -qO - https://downloads.osmocom.org/packages/osmocom:/latest/xUbuntu_24.04/Release.key \ |
| --- |
| │ gpg --dearmor \ |
| │ sudo tee /usr/share/keyrings/osmocom-latest.gpg > /dev/null |

### **Bloc 4 — Ajout depot sysmocom**

| echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/osmocom-latest.gpg] \ |
| --- |
| https://downloads.osmocom.org/packages/osmocom:/latest/xUbuntu_24.04/ ./" \ |
| │ sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/osmocom-latest.list |

### **Bloc 5 — Verification depot**

| sudo apt update 2>&1 │ grep -E "osmocom│Err│Hit│Get" |
| --- |
| apt-cache policy │ grep osmocom |

**Note : ***Resultat attendu : ligne downloads.osmocom.org avec code 500*

## **Etape 2/6 — Installation paquets coeur 2G**

| sudo apt install -y osmo-stp |
| --- |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-hlr |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-mgw |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-msc |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-sgsn |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-bsc |
| sudo apt install -y osmo-cbc |

### **Verification — 7 paquets**

| dpkg -l osmo-stp osmo-hlr osmo-mgw osmo-msc osmo-sgsn osmo-bsc osmo-cbc \ |
| --- |
| │ awk '/^[ih]i/{print $2, $3}' │ column -t |

## **Etape 3/6 — Fichiers de configuration (MCC=547)**

### **Bloc 0 — Repertoires**

| sudo mkdir -p /etc/osmocom /var/lib/osmocom |
| --- |

### **Bloc 1 — osmo-stp.cfg**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-stp.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoSTP  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
| bind 127.0.0.1 |
| cs7 instance 0 |
| description OsmoSTP-547-PLACEHOLDER |
| point-code 0.23.1 |
| listen m3ua 2905 |
| accept-asp-connections |
| local-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| EOF |

### **Bloc 2 — osmo-hlr.cfg**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-hlr.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoHLR  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
| bind 127.0.0.1 |
| hlr |
| database /var/lib/osmocom/hlr.db |
| gsup |
| bind ip 10.0.0.1 |
| bind port 4222 |
| EOF |

### **Bloc 3 — osmo-mgw.cfg**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-mgw.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoMGW  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
| bind 127.0.0.1 |
| mgcp |
| bind ip 10.0.0.1 |
| rtp bind-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| rtp port-range 16000 16999 |
| number endpoints 31 |
| EOF |

### **Bloc 4 — osmo-msc.cfg**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-msc.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoMSC  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
| bind 127.0.0.1 |
| network |
| network country code 547 |
| mobile network code PLACEHOLDER |
| short name OsmoNet |
| long name OsmoNet |
| msc |
| mgw remote-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| mgw remote-port 2427 |
| mgw reset-endpoint rtpbridge/*@mgw |
| hlr |
| remote-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| remote-port 4222 |
| cs7 instance 0 |
| point-code 0.23.3 |
| asp asp-clnt-msc 2905 0 m3ua |
| remote-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| role asp |
| sctp-role client |
| as as-clnt-msc m3ua |
| asp asp-clnt-msc |
| routing-key 2 0.23.3 |
| EOF |

### **Bloc 5 — osmo-sgsn.cfg**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-sgsn.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoSGSN  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
| bind 127.0.0.1 |
| sgsn |
| network country code 547 |
| mobile network code PLACEHOLDER |
| gtp local-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| auth-policy accept-all |
| ggsn 0 |
| remote-ip 10.0.0.1 |
| gtp-version 1 |
| no shutdown |
| ns |
| bind udp nse-main |
| listen 10.0.0.1 23000 |
| EOF |

### **Bloc 6 — osmo-bsc.cfg (base)**

| sudo tee /etc/osmocom/osmo-bsc.cfg > /dev/null << 'EOF' |
| --- |
| ! OsmoBSC  MCC=547  MNC=PLACEHOLDER |
| line vty |
| no login |
