| echo "net.ipv4.ip_forward=1" │ sudo tee -a /etc/sysctl.conf |
| sudo iptables-save │ grep MASQUERADE |

### **Bloc 5 — Firewall ports eNodeB**

| sudo ufw allow 36412/sctp comment 'S1AP eNodeB MME' |
| --- |
