### **Readiness check final Open5GS**

| echo '========== OPEN5GS READINESS CHECK ==========' |
| --- |
| ok=0 |
| for svc in mongod open5gs-hssd open5gs-pcrfd open5gs-sgwcd \ |
| open5gs-sgwud open5gs-smfd open5gs-upfd open5gs-mmed; do |
| [ "$(systemctl is-active $svc)" = 'active' ] && ok=$((ok+1)) |
| done |
| echo "Services actifs      : $ok/8" |
| sudo ss -tlnp │ grep -q 36412 && echo 'Port S1AP 36412 : OUVERT' ││ echo 'Port S1AP 36412 : FERME' |
| sudo ss -ulnp │ grep -q 2123  && echo 'Port GTP-C 2123 : OUVERT' ││ echo 'Port GTP-C 2123 : FERME' |
| sudo ss -ulnp │ grep -q 2152  && echo 'Port GTP-U 2152 : OUVERT' ││ echo 'Port GTP-U 2152 : FERME' |
| sudo ss -tlnp │ grep -q 3868  && echo 'Port Diameter   : OUVERT' ││ echo 'Port Diameter   : FERME' |
| ip link show ogstun │ grep -q 'UP' && echo 'ogstun          : UP'   ││ echo 'ogstun          : DOWN' |
| [ "$(cat /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward)" = '1' ] && echo 'IP forward      : OUI'  ││ echo 'IP forward      : NON' |
| sudo iptables -t nat -L POSTROUTING │ grep -q MASQUERADE && echo 'NAT MASQUERADE  : OK'  ││ echo 'NAT MASQUERADE  : MANQUANT' |
| echo '==============================================' |

